    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Notes on C++ for C# developers]]></title>
    <link href="http://zacg.github.io/blog/2013/05/29/notes-on-c-plus-plus--for-c-number-developers/"/>
    <updated>2013-05-29T02:25:00-04:00</updated>
